WEBVTT

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:00.440
is less than a year.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:04.575
This is a picture
of the George Mark Children's House,

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:08.096
the first pediatric
palliative respite care center

00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:10.376
to open in the United States.

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:13.376
I founded it in 2004,

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:16.336
after years of working as a psychologist

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:19.056
on pediatric intensive care units,

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:24.096
frustrated with the undignified deaths
that so many children experienced

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:26.040
and their families had to endure.

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:31.136
